<p>A <code>RedAmberGreenPickerButton</code> is one option inside
  a <a href="/components/red-amber-green-picker/"><code>RedAmberGreenPicker</code></a>.
  Each button is a <code>&lt;button role="radio"&gt;</code> with
  <code>data-status</code> and <code>aria-checked</code>.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/red-amber-green-picker/">Picker
  demo</a> for composed examples.</p>
